#: src/App/Model/Settings.php:874
msgid ""
"The Robot Exclusion Standard, also known as the Robots Exclusion Protocol "
"or\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t<code><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robots.txt\" "
"target=\"_blank\">robots.txt</a></code>\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tprotocol, is a convention for cooperating web crawlers and other "
"web robots\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tabout accessing all or part of a website that is otherwise "
"publicly viewable.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tYou can change it manually by editing <code>robots.txt</code> \n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tin your root WordPress directory."
msgstr ""
"Le protocole d&#39;exclusion des robots ( <code><a href=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Robots.txt\" target=\"_blank\">robots.txt</a></code> , "
"également appelé norme d&#39;exclusion des robots, est une convention "
"permettant aux robots d&#39;exploration et autres robots web de coopérer "
"concernant l&#39;accès à tout ou partie d&#39;un site web public. Vous "
"pouvez le modifier manuellement en éditant le <code>robots.txt</code> situé "
"à la racine de votre installation WordPress."

